be determined to be critical habitat as provided by section 4 of the Act, including adaptive management areas under
Alternative 9 of the Proposed Northwest Forest Plan; 

(2) The location and reasons why any non-Federal lands should or should not be determined to be critical habitat as
provided by section 4 of the Act, including potential threats and the value of any areas to the conservation of the species;






